                        <r3d:remarks>RADAR4Culture is based on the well-established data repository RADAR run by FIZ Karlsruhe - Leibniz Institute for Information Infrastructure (https://www.re3data.org/repository/r3d100012330). It was developed within the framework of FIZ Karlsruhe´s participation in the consortium for research data on tangible and intangible cultural assets NFDI4Culture (funded by German Research Foundation (DFG) - 441958017) within the german Nationale Forschungsdateninfrastruktur (NFDI). RADAR4Culture serves as a catch-all repository, which complements the already existing portfolio of subject specific repositories for cultural heritage research data and is e.g. ideally suited for cross-disciplinary data or datasets with a multitude of different data formats.</r3d:remarks>
